cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper deals with visual recognition and evaluation of models on large-scale datasets with noisy labels, which are common problems in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed framework involves active testing, which is a technique used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) to efficiently query a user for accurate performance estimates. The paper also mentions multi-label classification (cs.CL) and instance segmentation (cs.MM) as two popular computer vision tasks for which the proposed framework is effective.
